\cf0 The rules about syllogisms and definitions and classifications, on the other hand, greatly help people to understand, provided that they avoid the error of thinking that when they have mastered them they have learnt the actual truth about the happy life ( De Doctrina, Book Two, XXXVII55-XXXXVIII56).\super 2\nosupersub \
\
